{"data":{"article":{},"attachments":{},"author_id":"1741993395910811648","conversation_id":"1979825560894443828","created_at":"2025-10-19T19:46:10.000Z","edit_controls":{"editable_until":"2025-10-19T20:46:10.000Z","edits_remaining":5,"is_edit_eligible":false},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["1979997521607864354"],"entities":{"mentions":[{"end":16,"id":"1499709348616241155","start":0,"username":"caomeiweimaomao"}]},"geo":{},"id":"1979997521607864354","in_reply_to_user_id":"1499709348616241155","lang":"zh","note_tweet":{"entities":{}},"possibly_sensitive":false,"public_metrics":{"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"reply_count":0,"retweet_count":0},"referenced_tweets":[{"id":"1979825560894443828","type":"replied_to"}],"reply_settings":"everyone","text":"@caomeiweimaomao 绿十字我家两只猫一直吃，确实好用"},"includes":{"tweets":[{"article":{},"attachments":{},"author_id":"1741993395910811648","conversation_id":"1979825560894443828","created_at":"2025-10-19T19:46:10.000Z","edit_controls":{"editable_until":"2025-10-19T20:46:10.000Z","edits_remaining":5,"is_edit_eligible":false},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["1979997521607864354"],"entities":{"mentions":[{"end":16,"id":"1499709348616241155","start":0,"username":"caomeiweimaomao"}]},"geo":{},"id":"1979997521607864354","in_reply_to_user_id":"1499709348616241155","lang":"zh","note_tweet":{"entities":{}},"possibly_sensitive":false,"public_metrics":{"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"reply_count":0,"retweet_count":0},"referenced_tweets":[{"id":"1979825560894443828","type":"replied_to"}],"reply_settings":"everyone","text":"@caomeiweimaomao 绿十字我家两只猫一直吃，确实好用"},{"article":{},"attachments":{},"author_id":"1499709348616241155","conversation_id":"1979825560894443828","created_at":"2025-10-19T08:22:51.000Z","edit_controls":{"editable_until":"2025-10-19T09:22:51.000Z","edits_remaining":5,"is_edit_eligible":true},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["1979825560894443828"],"entities":{},"geo":{},"id":"1979825560894443828","lang":"zh","note_tweet":{"entities":{},"text":"来一点我搜集的小知识：\n1.家里猫猫吐毛严重可以买VET'S BEST绿十字猫草片，非常有用。\n2.蟑螂肆虐的话买拜耳或者科灭达的胶饵，尽可能滴在家里每个角落，最开始可能会一觉醒来一地……也不一定是一地的蟑螂尸体，但后面就不会了，至少好多年了我都没见过蟑螂。\n3.卡姿兰黑色那个散粉非常好用，然后也可以拍在嘴唇上，喝东西口红也不会被蹭掉。\n4.含氟的牙膏都可以美白牙齿没必要追求很贵的，但是一些人用了会导致下巴长痘。\n5.异维A酸软胶囊/阿达帕林凝胶都可以祛痘而且效果很明显，但是，一定，要去看三甲皮肤科医生不要瞎买瞎吃瞎涂，不然真的会烂脸诶，你们看不出来我初中因为痘痘很多被傻逼同学取绰号满天星吧反正。\n6.日常防晒霜非常推荐蜜丝婷泰版啊上脸不假白而且成膜快，军训这种高强度的日照就老老实实买安热沙吧。\n7.完美芦荟胶保湿也好消炎也好都很好用，前提是你买的是正版，大概五十？\n8.如果你上课上台演讲容易紧张的话，可以试试提前吃一颗普萘洛尔，能缓解心率过快的感觉。但你要是心率一直不对劲还是去看看医生吧。\n9.我家猫会开门，还会拉屎在外面，拉完还会象征性的扒拉几下嗯。"},"possibly_sensitive":false,"public_metrics":{"bookmark_count":1,"impression_count":851,"like_count":19,"quote_count":0,"reply_count":5,"retweet_count":0},"reply_settings":"everyone","text":"来一点我搜集的小知识：\n1.家里猫猫吐毛严重可以买VET'S BEST绿十字猫草片，非常有用。\n2.蟑螂肆虐的话买拜耳或者科灭达的胶饵，尽可能滴在家里每个角落，最开始可能会一觉醒来一地……也不一定是一地的蟑螂尸体，但后面就不会了，至少好多年了我都没见过蟑螂。"}],"users":[{"created_at":"2024-01-02T01:22:57.000Z","description":"猫，诗歌，精神动力学。艺术，朝闻道，波粒二象性。不断寻找着广播塔的星际候鸟。 | “我们彻夜飞旋，直至没入火焰。” | 匿名提问箱⬇️ | 🚪88/158","entities":{"url":{"urls":[{"display_url":"ngl.link/anincandescence","end":23,"expanded_url":"https://ngl.link/anincandescence","start":0,"url":"https://t.co/MuEKSg4tIS"}]}},"id":"1741993395910811648","location":"天鹅座X-1","name":"炽烈已极","pinned_tweet_id":"1976277813784457417","profile_image_url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1967287311504465922/Z7d-hW5p_normal.jpg","protected":false,"public_metrics":{"followers_count":1245,"following_count":212,"like_count":10924,"listed_count":3,"media_count":820,"tweet_count":4162},"url":"https://t.co/MuEKSg4tIS","username":"AnIncandescence","verified":false},{"created_at":"2022-03-04T11:32:32.000Z","description":"🎀写故事的 信则有不信则无 只是名为猫敷屋酱的碎碎念丨🦜嘤鹉：@SENDOH214丨🪜梯子https://t.co/ual3P7rvaQ","entities":{"description":{"mentions":[{"end":41,"start":31,"username":"SENDOH214"}],"urls":[{"display_url":"dash.lineasia.top/#/register?cod…","end":68,"expanded_url":"https://dash.lineasia.top/#/register?code=U8x8snvo","start":45,"ur